    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
別紙、乙（姉乙女）に送り候書状ハ、養子清次郎を論じて遣候事在<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>之候間、愚兄権平ニハ見せられぬ事おゝく候まゝ、必大兄御母上まで御送り愚兄ニハ小弟より手紙のあねニ達し候ことをしらせぬよふ御母上より御<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">直</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（じき）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ニ御達可<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>被<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>遣御願申上候。<lb />
<span rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">廿四日朝<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">頓首</span></span>
<lb />
望月清平様<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">才谷拝</span>
<span rend="jisage_5" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 5em">机下</span>
<lb />
